<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Package Order Created - DropSecure</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff8f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #800020 60%, #D4AF37 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }
        .tracking-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa 0%, #e9ecef 100%);
            border: 3px solid #800020;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .tracking-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #800020;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .package-details {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #800020;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #800020;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">DropSecure</div>
            <h2 style="margin: 0;">Package Order Created Successfully!</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h3>Hello <%= name %>,</h3>
            <p>Great news! A package delivery order has been created for you. Here are the details:</p>
            
            <div class="tracking-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #800020;">Your Tracking Number</h3>
                <div class="tracking-number"><%= trackingNumber %></div>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Save this number to track your package</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="package-details">
                <h4 style="color: #800020; margin-top: 0;">Package Details</h4>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Receiver:</span>
                    <span><%= receiverName %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Description:</span>
                    <span><%= packageDescription %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Estimated Delivery:</span>
                    <span><%= estimatedDeliveryDate %></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>You will receive notifications as your package moves through our delivery network. You can track your package in real-time using the tracking number above.</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= trackingUrl %>" class="cta-button">Track Your Package</a>
            </div>
            
            <p><strong>What's Next?</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li>Our team will process your package for pickup</li>
                <li>A courier will be assigned to your delivery</li>
                <li>You'll receive updates at each step of the delivery process</li>
                <li>The receiver will be notified when the package is ready for delivery</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>DropSecure - Secure Delivery Solutions</strong></p>
            <p>Questions? Contact our support team at support@dropsecure.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>